            <lg xml:id="TK767">
<l>tārtāṅkic celvatu tāṉai talaivanta</l>
<l>pōrtāṅkun taṉmai yaṟintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That is an army which knowing the art of warding off an impending struggle, can bear against the dust-van (of a hostile force).</l>
            </lg>
